---
// src/components/blog/InlineCTA.astro
---

<div class="inline-cta not-prose my-10 p-7 rounded-2xl text-center" style="background:rgba(175,77,152,0.06); border:1px solid rgba(175,77,152,0.15);">
    <p class="font-body font-bold text-lg mb-2" style="color:#8c3d79;">
        ¿Listo para tener tu página web?
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-5 max-w-[400px] mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        En Webix diseñamos sitios que convierten visitas en clientes.
        Presupuesto claro, mismo día.
    </p>
    <a href="https://wa.me/525650776884" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
       class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 no-underline font-bold text-sm text-white px-7 py-3 rounded-full"
       style="background:#AF4D98; box-shadow: 0 4px 0 #6b2d5a, 0 8px 16px rgba(175,77,152,0.25); transition: transform 0.18s cubic-bezier(0.34,1.56,0.64,1), box-shadow 0.18s ease;"
       onmouseover="this.style.transform='translateY(-3px)';this.style.boxShadow='0 7px 0 #6b2d5a, 0 14px 24px rgba(175,77,152,0.30)';"
       onmouseout="this.style.transform='';this.style.boxShadow='0 4px 0 #6b2d5a, 0 8px 16px rgba(175,77,152,0.25)';">
        Hablemos por WhatsApp ▶
    </a>
</div>
